{"tha-ap1:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap1:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap1:0.3":"Buddhaapadana ","tha-ap1:1.1":"Namo tassa Bhagavato Arahato Sammasambuddhassa. ","tha-ap1:2.1":"Tathagatam jetavane vasantam, ","tha-ap1:2.2":"Apucchi vedehamuni natango; ","tha-ap1:2.3":"“Sabbannubuddha kira nama honti, ","tha-ap1:2.4":"Bhavanti te hetubhi kehi vira”. ","tha-ap1:3.1":"Tadaha sabbannuvaro mahesi, ","tha-ap1:3.2":"Anandabhaddam madhurassarena; ","tha-ap1:3.3":"“Ye pubbabuddhesu katadhikara, ","tha-ap1:3.4":"Aladdhamokkha jinasasanesu. ","tha-ap1:4.1":"Teneva sambodhimukhena dhira, ","tha-ap1:4.2":"Ajjhasayenapi mahabalena; ","tha-ap1:4.3":"Pannaya tejena sutikkhapanna, ","tha-ap1:4.4":"Sabbannubhavam anupapunanti. ","tha-ap1:5.1":"Ahampi pubbabuddhesu, ","tha-ap1:5.2":"buddhattamabhipatthayim; ","tha-ap1:5.3":"Manasayeva hutvana, ","tha-ap1:5.4":"dhammaraja asankhiya. ","tha-ap1:6.1":"Atha buddhapadanani, ","tha-ap1:6.2":"sunatha suddhamanasa; ","tha-ap1:6.3":"Timsaparamisampunna, ","tha-ap1:6.4":"dhammaraja asankhiya. ","tha-ap1:7.1":"Sambodhim buddhasetthanam, ","tha-ap1:7.2":"sasanghe lokanayake; ","tha-ap1:7.3":"Dasanguli namassitva, ","tha-ap1:7.4":"sirasa abhivadayim. ","tha-ap1:8.1":"Yavata buddhakhettesu, ","tha-ap1:8.2":"ratana vijjantisankhiya; ","tha-ap1:8.3":"Akasattha ca bhumattha, ","tha-ap1:8.4":"manasa sabbamaharim. ","tha-ap1:9.1":"Tattha rupiyabhumiyam, ","tha-ap1:9.2":"pasadam mapayim aham; ","tha-ap1:9.3":"Nekabhummam ratanamayam, ","tha-ap1:9.4":"ubbiddham nabhamuggatam. ","tha-ap1:10.1":"Vicittathambham sukatam, ","tha-ap1:10.2":"suvibhattam maharaham; ","tha-ap1:10.3":"Kanakamayasanghatam, ","tha-ap1:10.4":"kontacchattehi manditam. ","tha-ap1:11.1":"Pathama veluriya bhumi, ","tha-ap1:11.2":"vimalabbhasama subha; ","tha-ap1:11.3":"Nalinajalajakinna, ","tha-ap1:11.4":"varakancanabhumiya. ","tha-ap1:12.1":"Pavalamsa pavalavanna, ","tha-ap1:12.2":"kaci lohitaka subha; ","tha-ap1:12.3":"Indagopakavannabha, ","tha-ap1:12.4":"bhumi obhasati disa. ","tha-ap1:13.1":"Suvibhatta gharamukha, ","tha-ap1:13.2":"niyyuha sihapanjara; ","tha-ap1:13.3":"Caturo vedika jala, ","tha-ap1:13.4":"gandhavela manorama. ","tha-ap1:14.1":"Nila pita lohitaka, ","tha-ap1:14.2":"odata suddhakalaka; ","tha-ap1:14.3":"Kutagaravarupeta, ","tha-ap1:14.4":"sattaratanabhusita. ","tha-ap1:15.1":"Olokamaya paduma, ","tha-ap1:15.2":"valavihangasobhita; ","tha-ap1:15.3":"Nakkhattatarakakinna, ","tha-ap1:15.4":"candasurehi mandita. ","tha-ap1:16.1":"Hemajalena sanchanna, ","tha-ap1:16.2":"sonnakinkinikayuta; ","tha-ap1:16.3":"Vatavegena kujanti, ","tha-ap1:16.4":"sonnamala manorama. ","tha-ap1:17.1":"Manjetthakam lohitakam, ","tha-ap1:17.2":"pitakam haripinjaram; ","tha-ap1:17.3":"Nanarangehi sampitam, ","tha-ap1:17.4":"ussitaddhajamalini. ","tha-ap1:18.1":"Na nam bahunekasata, ","tha-ap1:18.2":"phalika rajatamaya; ","tha-ap1:18.3":"Manimaya lohitanga, ","tha-ap1:18.4":"masaragallamaya tatha; ","tha-ap1:18.5":"Nanasayanavicitta, ","tha-ap1:18.6":"sanhakasikasanthata. ","tha-ap1:19.1":"Kampala dukula cina, ","tha-ap1:19.2":"pattunna pandupavura; ","tha-ap1:19.3":"Vividhattharanam sabbam, ","tha-ap1:19.4":"manasa pannapesaham. ","tha-ap1:20.1":"Tasu tasveva bhumisu, ","tha-ap1:20.2":"ratanakutalankatam; ","tha-ap1:20.3":"Maniverocana ukka, ","tha-ap1:20.4":"dharayanta sutitthare. ","tha-ap1:21.1":"Sobhanti esika thambha, ","tha-ap1:21.2":"subha kancanatorana; ","tha-ap1:21.3":"Jambonada saramaya, ","tha-ap1:21.4":"atho rajatamayapi ca. ","tha-ap1:22.1":"Neka sandhi suvibhatta, ","tha-ap1:22.2":"kavataggalacittita; ","tha-ap1:22.3":"Ubhato punnaghataneka, ","tha-ap1:22.4":"padumuppalasamyuta. ","tha-ap1:23.1":"Atite sabbabuddhe ca, ","tha-ap1:23.2":"sasanghe lokanayake; ","tha-ap1:23.3":"Pakativannarupena, ","tha-ap1:23.4":"nimminitva sasavake. ","tha-ap1:24.1":"Tena dvarena pavisitva, ","tha-ap1:24.2":"sabbe buddha sasavaka; ","tha-ap1:24.3":"Sabbasonnamaye pithe, ","tha-ap1:24.4":"nisinna ariyamandala. ","tha-ap1:25.1":"Ye ca etarahi atthi, ","tha-ap1:25.2":"Buddha loke anuttara; ","tha-ap1:25.3":"Atite vattamana ca, ","tha-ap1:25.4":"Bhavanam sabbe samaruhum. ","tha-ap1:26.1":"Paccekabuddhenekasate, ","tha-ap1:26.2":"Sayambhu aparajite; ","tha-ap1:26.3":"Atite vattamane ca, ","tha-ap1:26.4":"Bhavanam sabbe samaruhum. ","tha-ap1:27.1":"Kapparukkha bahu atthi, ","tha-ap1:27.2":"Ye dibba ye ca manusa; ","tha-ap1:27.3":"Sabbam dussam samahantva, ","tha-ap1:27.4":"Acchademi ticivaram. ","tha-ap1:28.1":"Khajjam bhojjam sayaniyam, ","tha-ap1:28.2":"sampannam panabhojanam; ","tha-ap1:28.3":"Manimaye subhe patte, ","tha-ap1:28.4":"sampuretva adasaham. ","tha-ap1:29.1":"Dibbavatthasama hutva, ","tha-ap1:29.2":"mattha civarasamyuta; ","tha-ap1:29.3":"Madhura sakkhara ceva, ","tha-ap1:29.4":"tela ca madhuphanita. ","tha-ap1:30.1":"Tappita paramannena, ","tha-ap1:30.2":"sabbe te ariyamandala; ","tha-ap1:30.3":"Ratanagabbham pavisitva, ","tha-ap1:30.4":"kesariva guhasaya. ","tha-ap1:31.1":"Maharahamhi sayane, ","tha-ap1:31.2":"sihaseyyamakappayum; ","tha-ap1:31.3":"Sampajana samutthaya, ","tha-ap1:31.4":"sayane pallankamabhujum. ","tha-ap1:32.1":"Gocaram sabbabuddhanam, ","tha-ap1:32.2":"jhanaratisamappita; ","tha-ap1:32.3":"Anne dhammani desenti, ","tha-ap1:32.4":"anne kilanti iddhiya. ","tha-ap1:33.1":"Anne abhinna appenti, ","tha-ap1:33.2":"abhinna vasibhavita; ","tha-ap1:33.3":"Vikubbana vikubbanti, ","tha-ap1:33.4":"annenekasahassiyo. ","tha-ap1:34.1":"Buddhapi buddhe pucchanti, ","tha-ap1:34.2":"visayam sabbannumalayam; ","tha-ap1:34.3":"Gambhiram nipunam thanam, ","tha-ap1:34.4":"pannaya vinibujjhare. ","tha-ap1:35.1":"Savaka buddhe pucchanti, ","tha-ap1:35.2":"buddha pucchanti savake; ","tha-ap1:35.3":"Annamannanca pucchitva, ","tha-ap1:35.4":"annonnam byakaronti te. ","tha-ap1:36.1":"Buddha paccekabuddha ca, ","tha-ap1:36.2":"savaka paricaraka; ","tha-ap1:36.3":"Evam sakaya ratiya, ","tha-ap1:36.4":"pasadebhiramanti te. ","tha-ap1:37.1":"Chatta titthantu ratana, ","tha-ap1:37.2":"kancanavelapantika; ","tha-ap1:37.3":"Muttajalaparikkhitta, ","tha-ap1:37.4":"sabbe dharentu matthake. ","tha-ap1:38.1":"Bhavantu celavitana, ","tha-ap1:38.2":"sonnatarakacittita; ","tha-ap1:38.3":"Vicittamalyavitata, ","tha-ap1:38.4":"sabbe dharentu matthake. ","tha-ap1:39.1":"Vitata malyadamehi, ","tha-ap1:39.2":"gandhadamehi sobhita; ","tha-ap1:39.3":"Dussadamaparikinna, ","tha-ap1:39.4":"ratanadamabhusita. ","tha-ap1:40.1":"Pupphabhikinna sucitta, ","tha-ap1:40.2":"surabhigandhabhusita; ","tha-ap1:40.3":"Gandhapancangulakata, ","tha-ap1:40.4":"hemacchadanachadita. ","tha-ap1:41.1":"Catuddisa pokkharanno, ","tha-ap1:41.2":"padumuppalasanthata; ","tha-ap1:41.3":"Sovannarupa khayantu, ","tha-ap1:41.4":"padmarenurajuggata. ","tha-ap1:42.1":"Pupphantu padapa sabbe, ","tha-ap1:42.2":"pasadassa samantato; ","tha-ap1:42.3":"Sayanca puppha muncitva, ","tha-ap1:42.4":"gantva bhavanamokirum. ","tha-ap1:43.1":"Sikhino tattha naccantu, ","tha-ap1:43.2":"dibbahamsa pakujare; ","tha-ap1:43.3":"Karavika ca gayantu, ","tha-ap1:43.4":"dijasangha samantato. ","tha-ap1:44.1":"Bheriyo sabba vajjantu, ","tha-ap1:44.2":"vina sabba rasantu ta; ","tha-ap1:44.3":"Sabba sangiti vattantu, ","tha-ap1:44.4":"pasadassa samantato. ","tha-ap1:45.1":"Yavata buddhakhettamhi, ","tha-ap1:45.2":"cakkavale tato pare; ","tha-ap1:45.3":"Mahanta jotisampanna, ","tha-ap1:45.4":"acchinna ratanamaya. ","tha-ap1:46.1":"Titthantu sonnapallanka, ","tha-ap1:46.2":"diparukkha jalantu te; ","tha-ap1:46.3":"Bhavantu ekapajjota, ","tha-ap1:46.4":"dasasahassiparampara. ","tha-ap1:47.1":"Ganika lasika ceva, ","tha-ap1:47.2":"naccantu accharagana; ","tha-ap1:47.3":"Nanaranga padissantu, ","tha-ap1:47.4":"pasadassa samantato. ","tha-ap1:48.1":"Dumagge pabbatagge va, ","tha-ap1:48.2":"sinerugirimuddhani; ","tha-ap1:48.3":"Ussapemi dhajam sabbam, ","tha-ap1:48.4":"vicittam pancavannikam. ","tha-ap1:49.1":"Nara naga ca gandhabba, ","tha-ap1:49.2":"sabbe deva upentu te; ","tha-ap1:49.3":"Namassanta panjalika, ","tha-ap1:49.4":"pasadam parivarayum. ","tha-ap1:50.1":"Yam kinci kusalam kammam, ","tha-ap1:50.2":"kattabbam kiriyam mama; ","tha-ap1:50.3":"Kayena vaca manasa, ","tha-ap1:50.4":"tidase sukatam katam. ","tha-ap1:51.1":"Ye satta sannino atthi, ","tha-ap1:51.2":"ye ca satta asannino; ","tha-ap1:51.3":"Katam punnaphalam mayham, ","tha-ap1:51.4":"sabbe bhagi bhavantu te. ","tha-ap1:52.1":"Yesam katam suviditam, ","tha-ap1:52.2":"dinnam punnaphalam maya; ","tha-ap1:52.3":"Ye ca tattha na jananti, ","tha-ap1:52.4":"deva gantva nivedayum. ","tha-ap1:53.1":"Sabbalokamhi ye satta, ","tha-ap1:53.2":"Jivantaharahetuka; ","tha-ap1:53.3":"Manunnam bhojanam sabbam, ","tha-ap1:53.4":"Labhantu mama cetasa. ","tha-ap1:54.1":"Manasa danam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap1:54.2":"manasa pasadamavahim; ","tha-ap1:54.3":"Pujita sabbasambuddha, ","tha-ap1:54.4":"pacceka jinasavaka. ","tha-ap1:55.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap1:55.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap1:55.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap1:55.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap1:56.1":"Duve bhave pajanami, ","tha-ap1:56.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","tha-ap1:56.3":"Annam gatim na janami, ","tha-ap1:56.4":"manasa patthanaphalam. ","tha-ap1:57.1":"Devanam adhiko homi, ","tha-ap1:57.2":"bhavami manujadhipo; ","tha-ap1:57.3":"Rupalakkhanasampanno, ","tha-ap1:57.4":"pannaya asamo bhave. ","tha-ap1:58.1":"Bhojanam vividham settham, ","tha-ap1:58.2":"Ratananca anappakam; ","tha-ap1:58.3":"Vividhani ca vatthani, ","tha-ap1:58.4":"Nabha khippam upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:59.1":"Pathabya pabbate ceva, ","tha-ap1:59.2":"akase udake vane; ","tha-ap1:59.3":"Yam yam hattham pasaremi, ","tha-ap1:59.4":"dibba bhakkha upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:60.1":"Pathabya pabbate ceva, ","tha-ap1:60.2":"akase udake vane; ","tha-ap1:60.3":"Yam yam hattham pasaremi, ","tha-ap1:60.4":"ratana sabbe upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:61.1":"Pathabya pabbate ceva, ","tha-ap1:61.2":"akase udake vane; ","tha-ap1:61.3":"Yam yam hattham pasaremi, ","tha-ap1:61.4":"sabbe gandha upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:62.1":"Pathabya pabbate ceva, ","tha-ap1:62.2":"akase udake vane; ","tha-ap1:62.3":"Yam yam hattham pasaremi, ","tha-ap1:62.4":"sabbe yana upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:63.1":"Pathabya pabbate ceva, ","tha-ap1:63.2":"akase udake vane; ","tha-ap1:63.3":"Yam yam hattham pasaremi, ","tha-ap1:63.4":"sabbe mala upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:64.1":"Pathabya pabbate ceva, ","tha-ap1:64.2":"akase udake vane; ","tha-ap1:64.3":"Yam yam hattham pasaremi, ","tha-ap1:64.4":"alankara upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:65.1":"Pathabya pabbate ceva, ","tha-ap1:65.2":"akase udake vane; ","tha-ap1:65.3":"Yam yam hattham pasaremi, ","tha-ap1:65.4":"sabba kanna upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:66.1":"Pathabya pabbate ceva, ","tha-ap1:66.2":"akase udake vane; ","tha-ap1:66.3":"Yam yam hattham pasaremi, ","tha-ap1:66.4":"madhusakkhara upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:67.1":"Pathabya pabbate ceva, ","tha-ap1:67.2":"akase udake vane; ","tha-ap1:67.3":"Yam yam hattham pasaremi, ","tha-ap1:67.4":"sabbe khajja upenti mam. ","tha-ap1:68.1":"Adhane addhikajane, ","tha-ap1:68.2":"yacake ca pathavino; ","tha-ap1:68.3":"Dadamiham danavaram, ","tha-ap1:68.4":"sambodhivarapattiya. ","tha-ap1:69.1":"Nadento pabbatam selam, ","tha-ap1:69.2":"gajjento bahalam girim; ","tha-ap1:69.3":"Sadevakam hasayanto, ","tha-ap1:69.4":"buddho loke bhavamaham. ","tha-ap1:70.1":"Disa dasavidha loke, ","tha-ap1:70.2":"yayato natthi antakam; ","tha-ap1:70.3":"Tasminca disabhagamhi, ","tha-ap1:70.4":"buddhakhetta asankhiya. ","tha-ap1:71.1":"Pabha pakittita mayham, ","tha-ap1:71.2":"yamaka ramsivahana; ","tha-ap1:71.3":"Etthantare ramsijalam, ","tha-ap1:71.4":"aloko vipulo bhave. ","tha-ap1:72.1":"Ettake lokadhatumhi, ","tha-ap1:72.2":"sabbe passantu mam jana; ","tha-ap1:72.3":"Sabbe mam anuvattantu, ","tha-ap1:72.4":"yava brahmanivesanam. ","tha-ap1:73.1":"Visitthamadhunadena, ","tha-ap1:73.2":"amatabherimahanim; ","tha-ap1:73.3":"Etthantare jana sabbe, ","tha-ap1:73.4":"sunantu madhuram giram. ","tha-ap1:74.1":"Dhammameghena vassante, ","tha-ap1:74.2":"sabbe hontu anasava; ","tha-ap1:74.3":"Yettha pacchimaka satta, ","tha-ap1:74.4":"sotapanna bhavantu te. ","tha-ap1:75.1":"Datva databbakam danam, ","tha-ap1:75.2":"silam puretva asesato; ","tha-ap1:75.3":"Nekkhammaparamim gantva, ","tha-ap1:75.4":"patto sambodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap1:76.1":"Pandite paripucchitva, ","tha-ap1:76.2":"katva viriyamuttamam; ","tha-ap1:76.3":"Khantiya paramim gantva, ","tha-ap1:76.4":"patto sambodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap1:77.1":"Katva dalhamadhitthanam, ","tha-ap1:77.2":"saccaparami puriya; ","tha-ap1:77.3":"Mettaya paramim gantva, ","tha-ap1:77.4":"patto sambodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap1:78.1":"Labhalabhe sukhe dukkhe, ","tha-ap1:78.2":"sammane cavamanane; ","tha-ap1:78.3":"Sabbattha samako hutva, ","tha-ap1:78.4":"patto sambodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap1:79.1":"Kosajjam bhayato disva, ","tha-ap1:79.2":"viriyancapi khemato; ","tha-ap1:79.3":"Araddhaviriya hotha, ","tha-ap1:79.4":"esa buddhanusasani. ","tha-ap1:80.1":"Vivadam bhayato disva, ","tha-ap1:80.2":"avivadanca khemato; ","tha-ap1:80.3":"Samagga sakhila hotha, ","tha-ap1:80.4":"esa buddhanusasani. ","tha-ap1:81.1":"Pamadam bhayato disva, ","tha-ap1:81.2":"appamadanca khemato; ","tha-ap1:81.3":"Bhavethatthangikam maggam, ","tha-ap1:81.4":"esa buddhanusasani. ","tha-ap1:82.1":"Samagata bahu buddha, ","tha-ap1:82.2":"arahanta ca sabbaso; ","tha-ap1:82.3":"Sambuddhe arahante ca, ","tha-ap1:82.4":"vandamana namassatha. ","tha-ap1:83.1":"Evam acintiya buddha, ","tha-ap1:83.2":"buddhadhamma acintiya; ","tha-ap1:83.3":"Acintiye pasannanam, ","tha-ap1:83.4":"vipako hoti acintiyo”. ","tha-ap1:84.1":"Ittham sudam bhagava attano buddhacariyam sambhavayamano buddhapadaniyam nama dhammapariyayam abhasitthati. ","tha-ap1:85.1":"Buddhapadanam samattam. "}